---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Terms of Use — Global Wealth Portfolio">
  <section class="container-page pt-3xl pb-2xl max-w-3xl">
    <p class="text-caption-mono text-body mb-xs">Legal</p>
    <h1 class="text-display-lg mb-lg">Terms of use</h1>
    <p class="text-body-md text-body mb-md">
      By using Global Wealth Portfolio, you agree to these terms. If you do not
      agree, please don't use the app.
    </p>
    <h2 class="text-display-md mt-2xl mb-md">No financial advice</h2>
    <p class="text-body-md text-body mb-md">
      Global Wealth Portfolio is a tracking tool. It does not provide
      investment, tax, legal, or financial advice. All projections, returns, and
      benchmarks are illustrative. Please consult a SEBI-registered (or your
      local jurisdiction's equivalent) financial advisor before making
      investment decisions.
    </p>
    <h2 class="text-display-md mt-2xl mb-md">No warranty</h2>
    <p class="text-body-md text-body mb-md">
      The app is provided "as is" without any warranty of any kind. We do not
      guarantee the accuracy of OCR results, benchmark data, or projections. You
      are responsible for verifying all data.
    </p>
    <h2 class="text-display-md mt-2xl mb-md">Data responsibility</h2>
    <p class="text-body-md text-body mb-md">
      Your data is stored in your browser. We do not back it up for you. If you
      clear your browser data, switch browsers, or use a different device, your
      data will not follow. Use the export feature regularly.
    </p>
    <h2 class="text-display-md mt-2xl mb-md">Open source</h2>
    <p class="text-body-md text-body mb-md">
      The app is open source. You can inspect, fork, and run your own copy.
    </p>
    <h2 class="text-display-md mt-2xl mb-md">Limitation of liability</h2>
    <p class="text-body-md text-body mb-md">
      We are not liable for any losses or damages arising from use of the app,
      including but not limited to financial losses from investment decisions
      based on app data.
    </p>
    <h2 class="text-display-md mt-2xl mb-md">Changes</h2>
    <p class="text-body-md text-body">
      We may update these terms at any time. Continued use constitutes
      acceptance.
    </p>
  </section>
</Layout>
